```diff
              img.src = svgFile;
          }
+ 
+         function downloadAllIcons() {
+             const allIcons = [
+                 // Standard icons
+                 { svg: 'icon-base.svg', size: 72, name: 'icon-72x72.png' },
+                 { svg: 'icon-base.svg', size: 96, name: 'icon-96x96.png' },
+                 { svg: 'icon-base.svg', size: 128, name: 'icon-128x128.png' },
+                 { svg: 'icon-base.svg', size: 144, name: 'icon-144x144.png' },
+                 { svg: 'icon-base.svg', size: 152, name: 'icon-152x152.png' },
+                 { svg: 'icon-base.svg', size: 192, name: 'icon-192x192.png' },
+                 { svg: 'icon-base.svg', size: 384, name: 'icon-384x384.png' },
+                 { svg: 'icon-base.svg', size: 512, name: 'icon-512x512.png' },
+                 // Maskable icons
+                 { svg: 'icon-maskable-base.svg', size: 192, name: 'icon-maskable-192x192.png' },
+                 { svg: 'icon-maskable-base.svg', size: 512, name: 'icon-maskable-512x512.png' },
+                 // Shortcut icons
+                 { svg: 'task-shortcut.svg', size: 96, name: 'task-shortcut.png' },
+                 { svg: 'profile-shortcut.svg', size: 96, name: 'profile-shortcut.png' },
+                 { svg: 'analytics-shortcut.svg', size: 96, name: 'analytics-shortcut.png' }
+             ];
+ 
+             let currentIndex = 0;
+             const downloadNext = () => {
+                 if (currentIndex >= allIcons.length) {
+                     alert('🎉 All icons downloaded successfully!');
+                     return;
+                 }
+                 
+                 const icon = allIcons[currentIndex];
+                 downloadIcon(icon.svg, icon.size, icon.name);
+                 currentIndex++;
+                 
+                 // Add small delay between downloads
+                 setTimeout(downloadNext, 500);
+             };
+             
+             downloadNext();
+         }
      </script>
  </body>
```
